title: Ep. 1027 - Democrats Are The Party Of Amber Heard
description:
Biden’s fully vaxxed HHS secretary contracts COVID for the second time in 25 days, Biden blames Republicans for inflation, and New York’s highest court rules that elephants aren't people.

Watch our Summer blockbuster “Terror on the Prairie” with Gina Carano: https://utm.io/ueFOe
